txt.en: Your continued efforts to aid the Kintai Elves brings great joy to them. You should visit Thridarlan at Shonith to receive a gift from the Elves of the oasis.
Visit Thridarlan at Shonith to receive a gift
Your standing with the Adúrhid improves and earns you a gift from the Ikorbâni Elves.

'We cannot express how strange it is to have you help us. When our people refused to heed the call to the west we did not think we would ever see our cousins again.

'Now, we find an ally in you.

'I wonder, how unique are you among the Eldar?

'Unique or not, we are pleased you seek to aid us still. You are a noble ally.'
Your continued assistance with the goals and objective of the Kintai Elves earns you merit among them. They wish to honour your efforts with a gift at Shonith.
Reach Ally tier with the Adúrhid

'We find you an interesting ally. We are not accustomed to finding allies, but we are very pleased that we have an ally in you.\n\n'Our offerings are meager, I fear, but they are gifted with the same measure of kindness you have shown us.'
Your continued assistance with the goals and objective of the Kintai Elves earns you merit among them. They wish to honour your efforts with a gift at Shonith.
